  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Codd\" title=\"House Codd\"><img alt=\"House Codd 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/50px-House_Codd_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/75px-House_Codd_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/100px-House_Codd_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Eldred Codd</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Codd\" title=\"House Codd\"><img alt=\"House Codd 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/50px-House_Codd_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/75px-House_Codd_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Codd_2.svg/100px-House_Codd_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Codd\" title=\"House Codd\">House Codd</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Eldred Codd</b> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider and a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Codd\" title=\"House Codd\">House Codd</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eldred_Codd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eldred_Codd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>, Eldred dances the <a href=\"/index.php/Finger_dance\" title=\"Finger dance\">finger dance</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_the_Maid\" title=\"Qarl the Maid\">Qarl the Maid</a>. One of his fingers is cut off and lands in <a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_the_Limper\" title=\"Ralf the Limper\">Ralf the Limper</a>'s drink.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> After <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> confront each other, Eldred departs the tent with his bloodied hand.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Eldred_Codd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, The Iron Captain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403135444\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.062 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.240 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 500/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10428/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4762/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 216/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 813/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  231.935      1 -total\n 97.11%  225.231      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.25%  223.232      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.62%   26.962     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.49%    8.093      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.19%    5.073      2 Template:Ref\n  1.41%    3.270      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.62%    1.430      1 Template:References\n  0.43%    0.986      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- 